<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Is this a scam?</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://localhost:80/home.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <% error.forEach(error => { %>
            <% if(error)    { %>
                <p><%= error%></p>
            <% } %>
        <% }) %>
        <% scams.forEach(scam => { %>
            <% if(scam)    { %>
                <% if(scam == 3)    { %>
                    <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
                        This website is trusted!
                    </div>
                <% } else if(scam == 1)    { %>
                    <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                        This website is proved as scam!
                    </div>
                <% } else if(scam == 2)    { %>
                    <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
                        We don't know this website.
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            <% } %>
        <% }) %>
    </div>

    <center class="container">
        <div class="header p-5 mb-4 bg-dark rounded-3">
            <h1>Is this a scam?</h1>
            <h3>Check for scam in the internet and prevent being hacked or scammed.</h3>

            <form action="/isscam" method="post">
            <input type="text" name="url" id="" class="form-control gray" style="border: none; color: #fff;" placeholder="your.url"></form>
        </div>
    

        <h3>How we're doing it</h3>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <br>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <h3>User-Based Anti-Scam</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <p>Our users can report something. Other uses we trust will check if the link is scam.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 order-md-2">
                <h3>Chrome Extension</h3>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <p>We developed a chrome extension which prevents you to go on an reported scam site.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </center>   


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>